{"tid":1781171,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(發現新大陸) 原來立法會民主派只得15個議席","createTime":"2019-12-13T03:06:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-13T03:10:41.000Z","uid":286206,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"df93ec3bdd5fb83e0462fe60e4fb3782370e8e8c","tid":1781171,"uid":286206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T03:06:57.000Z","msg":"6會財委會今早（12月13日）繼續審議公務員加薪撥款，民主派要求將警隊加薪建議分拆，又要求警方出席會議，接受提問。  財委會隨後表決，是否傳召警務處處長鄧炳強<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">列席會議，動議僅得15票贊成、30票反對遭否決</span></strong></span>。  公務員事務局局長羅智光表示，今次撥款只是涉及公務員薪級表的調整，而部門和職系表現，並非調整公務員薪酬的考慮因素，因此毋須其他局或部門出席。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地2020 年一定要建制派大敗"},{"pid":"182f294b2c4d7fad9ff160f2fc5966ce57c3a902","tid":1781171,"uid":264071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T03:10:41.000Z","msg":"真係發現新大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}